fields.name: CancelDate
fields.description: Date and time in UTC of when the terms were cancelled. This is empty if state is active.

fields.name: Id
fields.description: A unique identifier of the agreement.

fields.name: Offer
fields.description: Offer identifier string of image being deployed.

fields.name: Publisher
fields.description: Publisher identifier string of image being deployed.

fields.name: SignDate
fields.description: Date and time in UTC of when the terms were accepted. This is empty if state is cancelled.

fields.name: State
fields.description: Whether the agreement is active or cancelled
